thread.title: Treasury Will Sell $101 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury Will Sell $101 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. will auction $101 billion in securities next week, comprising $42 billion in new debt and $59 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Aug. 17, 2017, maturing Aug. 16, 2018. Cusip number: 912796NQ8.
Also, $42 billion...
